data.description: This lovely one-story house is situated in a wonderful neighborhood just north of San Antonio, close to and with easy access to excellent dining, shopping, and employment opportunities. There is a park, pool, and golf course in the neighborhood. The San Antonio Airport, medical facilities, and Joint Military Bases are all only a few miles away.
